title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Sep 10 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Sep 10 2022
description:
Gavin Newsom and California Democrats ramp up the authoritarianism amid the power failure. One European official even used the term "flatten the curve" to discuss the energy crisis. Mark Cuban slings arrows at Pocahontas. Senator Ron Johnson explains to Clay and Buck how the FBI tried to smear him as a Russian agent. NYT: Democrats fret over Stacey Abrams' struggles in Georgia.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
